comment._content:
I too wonder if the 'Fraser' is a transcription error.
London gazette August 8th 1908:

&quot;The Waterford Garrison Artillery. Lieutenant Edward F. Frazer to be Captain. Dated 13th August 1908.&quot;

And he had been promoted from 2nd Lieutenant to Lieutenant on 11th Feb 1905

London Gazette, May5th, 1903: &quot;The Waterford. Edward Francis Frazer, Gent.., to be Second Lieutenant. Dated 17th April, 1903.&quot;
